2b76a911-5692-4405-a5ba-ad2ee1a1804d.message: Blessed #is the man who, having nothing to say, abstains from giving us wordy evidence of the fact.

2b92d325-ce41-449c-93f7-455b539d6ecd.message: I can't understand why people are frightened by new #ideas. I'm frightened of old ones.

2bc888df-f3db-4894-b315-f1c1cc0b51ee.message: There are some days when I just don't feel #like talking.. Today is that day.
